Info
====

Run 'sh bootstrap.sh' first if starting with a fresh checkout.


General
=======

./configure
make

With Timbl support, local install:

./configure --prefix=/home/pberck/local --with-timbl=/home/pberck/local
make
export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=$LD_LIBRARY_PATH:/home/pberck/local/lib

OS X
====

./configure --with-timbl=/Users/pberck/install/

Debian 
======

export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=$LD_LIBRARY_PATH:/home/pberck/local/lib


Example:
--------

Perplexiteitsberekeningen:

wopr -r pplxs -p filename:reuters.martin.tok.10000.test.ng4,lexicon:reuters.martin.tok.10000.train.lex,ibasefile:reuters.martin.tok.10000.train.ng4.ibase,ws:4,timbl:"-a1 +D",counts:reuters.martin.tok.10000.train.cnt 

wopr -r pplxs -p filename:testset.ws3,lexicon:reuters.martin.tok.1000.lex,ibasefile:reuters.martin.tok.1000.ws3.ibase,ws:3,timbl:"-a1 +D"

